      <p>Trigger event subject lines reference a recent, verifiable event involving the recipient or their company. These achieve the highest open rates because they demonstrate real-time awareness and create immediate relevance. The trade-off is scalability&mdash;identifying trigger events requires either manual research or sophisticated event-monitoring tools.</p>

